Solidworks Training by CMED and MSS
===================================

by [cmedpic](https://fke.utm.my/author/cmedpic/ "Posts by cmedpic")
 | Oct 11, 2020 | [CMED](https://fke.utm.my/category/cmed/)

![](https://fke.utm.my/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WhatsApp-Image-2020-10-13-at-11.51.29-AM-1-1000x675.jpeg)

Two-day training on Solidworks CAD Drawing was organised by CMED Division and co-organised by Malaysian Simulation Society (MSS) on 11t to 12th October 2020.
